## 11. Tone of Voice

| Attribute | Description |
|---|---|
| **Confident** | We know the problem. We built the solution. |
| **Conversational** | Talk like a fellow creator, not a startup. |
| **Aspirational** | Celebrate what creators can achieve, not just features. |
| **India-proud** | Celebrate the INR. Celebrate settling locally. |
| **Action-oriented** | Every sentence moves the creator forward. |

**Avoid:** Corporate jargon, passive voice, vague claims, "revolutionizing" / "disrupting".

---

## 12. Open Questions for Founder Input

- [ ] What is the current pricing / free plan structure?
- [ ] Is there a public testimonial or case study from early users?
- [ ] Which site type is most popular / best to lead with in ads?
- [ ] Is there a referral incentive for creators who bring other creators?
- [ ] What is the target creator follower count — micro (10k-100k) or mid-tier (100k+)?
- [ ] Is the domain digione.ai finalized for all public-facing URLs?
